name: Jaguar Plastic Industries
description: exporter and wholesaler of a qualitative
overview:
Jaguar Plastic Industries came into existence as a sole proprietorship firm, in the 2011. The organization has started its business as a manufacturer, exporter, wholesaler and supplier of a comprehensive range of MCB Enclosures, Fan Boxes, Oil Cans, Junction Boxes, Plastic Tops, Plastic Jars, Bottle & Jar Caps and Plastic Bottles. Products come under these categories are 1 Ltr Cosmetic HDPE Bottles, 1 Ltr HDPE Water Bottles, 1 Ltr Narrow Mouth Bottles, Compressor Caps, 1 Ltr HDPE Jar Caps, 1 Ltr Pickle Jars, 1 Ltr HDPE Oil Cans and many more.

Our Products: Plastic Jars Bottle Tops Junction Boxes Oil Cans

Our Team: Our company is having the support of highly experienced and knowledgeable team of professionals. They are well-versed with the growing market requirements and make persistent endeavor to supply products and solutions accordingly.

Our Quality Assurance: Our commitment towards excellence is clearly reflected in the entire product range offered by us. For this, we are following streamlined and strict quality control measures, which help us in delivering error free products in the market.

Our Infrastructure: The complete production activity and other operations are smoothly and swiftly carried out in our hi-tech infrastructural set-up. It spread over a huge area of land as well as segregated into varied other departments such as production, quality control, research and development and many others.
